I love this recipe. I've made it twice already. I think it's a perfect summer (almost) no-cook recipe. To fix the dressing problem of the previous reviewer, add the water that is recommended. The first time I made it I didn't add water and it was dry. The second time I did add it and though it seemed too runny immediately after adding the water, the pasta and fish absorbed and left a nice creamy dressing.

